.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, helicopter, trike, subway
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, january, june, september, april
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: motorbikemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, folk, r&b, gospel, pop
1. the person who's birthday is in october is the person driving the helicopter
2. the person who's birthday is in swedish is the fan of r&b
3. the person who's birthday is in january is the person drinking tea
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the trike
5. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking coffee
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the fan of folk
7. the person driving the subway is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of salsa
11. the fan of pops is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the motorbikemaster-smoker is the person drinking beer
13. the person who's birthday is in june is the prince-smoker
14. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Transport		|    subway	|     motorbike	|      helicopter	|     scooter	|     trike	|
| Birthday	|   september	|    january	|    october	|    june	|    swedish	|
| Music-Genre		|     salsa	|    pop	|     folk	|     gospel	|      r&b	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   motorbikemaster	|
